	(231, 0, '2', 129, '1', '15', NULL, '-	Direktorat Jenderal Perkeretaapian Kementerian Perhubungan\r\n-	DKI JAKARTA\r\n-	PT. MRT JAKARTA', 2012, 'Engineering Services Jakarta Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) East-West Line Phase I Project', 'Kegiatan Jasa Konsultansi Jakarta Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) East-  West Fase 1', '1) Route and network planning of Jakarta MRT East-West System for Kembangan-Ujung Menteng Section considering the further network integration with the existing and the future public transportation networks;\r\n2) Demand forecast review and analysis, considering the operating Trans-Jakarta Busway System, Monorail system and future public transport and feeder system concept along the planned MRT System corridor;\r\n3) Transport capacity and operation planning, including executing staging analysis and program;\r\n4) Detailed route surveys including geological survey, topographic survey, utility survey and others, and land prepa+ration planning and implementing procedures;\r\n5) Design and engineering analysis for infrastructure construction, system facilities installation and rolling stocks procurement, including the operation and maintenance management system plans;\r\n6) Environmental impact assessment, including natural and social aspects, land requirements and human and area resettlement along the planned corridor and right of way and so on;\r\n7) Implementation planning, including analysis on the demarcation of roles by Central Government and DKI Jakarta Regional Government, MRT System operation and maintenance organizational structures and their establishment and private sectors participation;\r\n8) Investment planning and analysis, including funds requirement and schedule, source of finances, and their application and private investors participation;\r\n9) Economic and financial impact analysis and evaluation, including MRT System tariff method and financial operating planning;\r\n10) Prequalification and Tender documents preparation based on Design Build Contract, including contract lots analysis and project execution plan.', '1) Rute dan jaringan perencanaan sistem MRT East-West untuk Kembangan-Ujung Menteng  dengan mempertimbangkan integrasi jaringan dengan yang ada dan jaringan transportasi publik masa depan;\r\n2) Prakiraan  review dan analisis permintaan, mengingat sistem  operasi Busway Trans-Jakarta, Monorail dan sistem transportasi umum masa depan dan konsep sistem feeder sepanjang perencanaan koridor Sistem MRT;\r\n3) Perencanaan operasi dan kapasitas transportasi , termasuk tahapan pelaksanaan analisis dan program;\r\n4) Survei rute  termasuk survei geologi, survei topografi, survei utilitas dan lain-lain, serta persiapan lahan dan posedur pelaksanaan;\r\n5) Desain dan analisis rekayasa untuk pembangunan infrastruktur, pemasangan sistem fasilitas dan pengadaan sarana perkeretaapian, termasuk rencana  pengelolaan sistem operasi dan pemeliharaan ;\r\n6) Analisis dampak lingkungan, termasuk aspek alam dan sosial, kebutuhan manusia dan lahan serta area pemukiman sepanjang rencana koridor dan sebagainya;\r\n7) Pelaksanaan perencanaan, termasuk analisis mengenai demarkasi peran oleh Pemerintah Pusat dan Pemerintah Daerah DKI Jakarta, sistem operasi MRT dan struktur  organisasi pemeliharaannya  serta adanya partisipasi sektor swasta;\r\n8) Analisis dan perencanaan investasi, termasuk kebutuhan dana dan waktu, sumber pendanaan, serta aplikasi dan partisipasi investor swasta;\r\n9) Evaluasi dan analisis dampak ekonomi dan keuangan, termasuk metode tarif MRT Sistem dan rencana operasi financial;\r\n10) Prakualifikasi dan persiapan dokumen tender berdasarkan Kontrak Design Bulid, termasuk analisis kontrak jamak dan rencana pelaksanaan.', 14, 2012, '', '', '1) Pembentukan sistem MRT East – West Line;\r\n2) Sistem jaringan terpadu MRT East - West dan North - South.', '1) Memaksimalkan layanan perkeretaapian yang ada serta sistem MRT yang direncanakan;\r\n2) Berkontribusi untuk meningkatkan sistem transportasi publik