	(163, '23', '', 'Dirjen Cipta Karya', '19', 2016, 'The Improvement of Solid Waste Management to Support Regional Area and Metropolitan Cities', 'The Improvement of Solid Waste Management to Support Regional Area and Metropolitan Cities', 'a. Rehabilitation and reengineering of existing landfills, the development of new Sanitary Landfill which is completed with leachate treatment installation, heavy equipment such as bulldozers and compactor, and facilitieas for staff/operator,\r\nb. The development of the Intermediate Treatment Facility (ITF),\r\nc. The development of Reuse, Reduce, and Recycle (3R),\r\nd. Capacity building for waste treatment.', 'a. Rehabilitation and reengineering of existing landfills, the development of new Sanitary Landfill which is completed with leachate treatment installation, heavy equipment such as bulldozers and compactor, and facilitieas for staff/operator,\r\nb. The development of the Intermediate Treatment Facility (ITF),\r\nc. The development of Reuse, Reduce, and Recycle (3R),\r\nd. Capacity building for waste treatment.', 100000000, 0, 2015, 24, 'a. The completion of technical construction of  sanitary landfill and its supporting infrastructure which  serves 4 million persons\r\nb. Contract for operation and maintenance (O&M),\r\nc. The adoption and implementation of O&M system and guidelines,\r\nd. The improvement of waste collection and disposal level,\r\ne. The adoption and implementation of pricing and collection strategies.', 'a. The establishment of sustainable solid waste management system,\r\nb. The reduction of direct landfilling,\r\nc. A longer service period of the landfill\r\nd. Smaller amount of greenhouse gas emissions.', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '', 'undefined', 1, 1, 1, 0, '0', '3,15,31', '23,204,429'),
