	(170, '23', '', 'Ditjen Sumber Daya Air', '5', 2016, 'Modernization Strategic Irrigation Project of Indonesia (MSIP)', 'Modernization Strategic Irrigation Project of Indonesia (MSIP)', 'The proposed project includes \r\ni) Review of system planning of each scheme, \r\nii) Detailed design or review\r\ndesign of the main & secondary irrigation/ drainage systems, \r\niii) SID of tertian; systems, \r\niv) Modernization/ Upgrdingl Rehabilitation works of the existing barrage, main & secondary irrigation\r\nsystems, drainage systems, etc., and\r\n v) Soft Component.', 'The proposed project includes \r\ni) Review of system planning of each scheme, \r\nii) Detailed design or review\r\ndesign of the main & secondary irrigation/ drainage systems, \r\niii) SID of tertian; systems, \r\niv) Modernization/ Upgrdingl Rehabilitation works of the existing barrage, main & secondary irrigation\r\nsystems, drainage systems, etc., and\r\n v) Soft Component.', 278355000, 0, 2015, 72, 'a. Modernization/ Upgrading! Rehabilitation of the existing irrigation schemes\r\nb. Improvement of irrigation system: 198,459 ha including some extension of32,586 ha\r\nc. Modernization! Upgrading! Rehabilitation of the existing headworks\r\nd. Modernization of main & seoncary irrigation canals by lining\r\ne. Recovery of original function by de-silting of main & secondary irrigation canals\r\nf Improvement of drainage system\r\ng. Tertiary development\r\nh. Soft component: i) Institutional strengthening of government O&M organization, ii) Activation of\r\nWater Users\' Association, iii) Improvement of water distribution/ management and iv) Asset\r\nmanagement', 'a. Sufficient water distribution to 198,459 ha even in the dry season including some extension of 32,586\r\nha.\r\nb. Decrease of the present high water loss by means of imroving the present irrigation efficiency of some\r\n45% to more than 65% as originally designed.\r\nc. Increase of the cropping intensity of paddy Increase of the productivity 