	(172, '23', '', 'Ditjen Sumber Daya Air', '14', 2017, 'Integrated Citarum Water Resources Management Investment Program II', 'Integrated Citarum Water Resources Management Investment Program II', 'a) Develop bulk survace water sources for greater Bandung mtd reduce dependency on groundwater; ,\r\nb) Implement bulik water supply options in the upper catchments around Bandung to fulfil future bulk \'\r\nwater demands of greater Bandung;\r\nc) Soil conservation in upper watershed areas, targeting crucial catchments that will provile bulk water;\r\nd) Introduce suitable holticulture and forestry sctivities in critical, erosion prone lands around Bandung\r\nin order to reduce soil erosion, conserve water resources and improve bulk water supply; and\r\ne) Prepare following periodic financing request', 'a) Develop bulk survace water sources for greater Bandung mtd reduce dependency on groundwater; ,\r\nb) Implement bulik water supply options in the upper catchments around Bandung to fulfil future bulk \'\r\nwater demands of greater Bandung;\r\nc) Soil conservation in upper watershed areas, targeting crucial catchments that will provile bulk water;\r\nd) Introduce suitable holticulture and forestry sctivities in critical, erosion prone lands around Bandung\r\nin order to reduce soil erosion, conserve water resources and improve bulk water supply; and\r\ne) Prepare following periodic financing request', 200000000, 0, 2015, 60, '1. Constructed new raw water supply systems for approximately 1.5 m3/s;\r\n2. Improved upper watershed management; and\r\n3. Design for follow up PFRs', '1. Increased raw water supply in Bandung and surrounding areas;\r\n2. Reduced groundwater stress;\r\n3. Reduced soil erosion in the upper watershed;\r\n4. Lower sediment loads in the Citarum River; and\r\n5. Improved recharge of ground aquifer.', 20000000, 1, 0, 0, 0, '', 'undefined', 3, 1, 1, 0, '0', '9', 'null'),
	(173, '23', '', 'Ditjen Sumber Daya Air', '14', 2019, 'Karian Dam-Serpong Water Conveyance and Supply System Project', 'Karian Dam-Serpong Water Conveyance and Supply System Project', 'i) Construct of KSCS , pipe line with length 20,6 km and 15,4 km (D2000-2lanes)\r\nii) Construct of KSCS 2, pipe line with length 11,9 km (D1650-2lanes)\r\niii) Consultant Supervision\r\niv) Conducting operation and maintenance', 'i) Construct of KSCS , pipe line with length 20,6 km and 15,4 km (D2000-2lanes)\r\nii) Construct of KSCS 2, pipe line with length 11,9 km (D1650-2lanes)\r\niii) Consultant Supervision\r\niv) Conducting operation and maintenance', 373861700, 0, 2015, 60, 'Development of water conveyance and supply system in project area will contribute to supply 14.6 m3/s\r\nwater to the service areas, which is 10.6 m3/s will be allocated for DMI (Domestic, Municipal and •\r\nIndustry) and 4.0 m3/s for in·igation uses. It will supply about 33% of the water demand in the service\r\nareas.', 'a. Increased raw water supply in Banten, West Jakarta and surrounding areas;\r\nb. Reduced groundwater exploration', 181074000, 1, 0, 0, 0, '', 'undefined', 3, 1, 1, 0, '0', '3,6', 'null'),
