\n\r\nc. Supervision of Vessel Construction\r\nDuring the construction and the installation of research instrument will be supervised by the\r\nIndonesian Consultants both government and private agencies.\r\n\r\n\r\nd. Training and Familiarization\r\nThe activities of training and familiarization of the vessel and research instrument  will be given to the crew, technicians/ operators and researchers who will be assigned to operate the vessel and research equipment.\r\n\r\n\r\ne. Testing,Commissioning and Handover\r\nBefore conducting the handover of the vessel, the shipyard is required to conduct some testing on the ship that have been built and all the equipment that were mounted on it.', 107950000, 0, 2016, 36, 'The availability of two  (2) Units multi-functions  Research Vessel (1500 GT per unit) QUALITY international standards', 'a.	Increased capacity and capability of Indonesian researchers in the maritime sector;\r\nb. 	Increasing and strengthening the role of marine science in the development of maritime in\r\nIndonesia;\r\nc.	Increased use of marine resources;\r\nd. 	Increased Quality, Carrying Capacity and Sustainability of the Marine Environment\r\nFunction;\r\ne. 	Increased insight and Maritime Culture', 2950000, 1, 0, 0, 0, '', 'undefined', 14, 1, 1, 0, '26', 'null', 'null'),
